<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07458</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING SECTIONS 20, 22, 27, 28, 34, 40, 50, 73, 112, 119, 203, 204, 220, 222, 228, 237, 237-A, 248, 254, 255, 256, 257, 258, 259, 260, 261, 262, 263, 264, 265, 266, 275, 290, 291, 292 AND ADDING SECTIONS 293, 294, 295, 296, 297, 298, 298-A, 299, 300, 301, 302, 303, 304, 305, AND 306 UNDER CHAPTERS I, II, III, IV, V AND VI, ALL UNDER THE NATIONAL INTERNAL REVENUE CODE OF 1997, AS AMENDED, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Complements the Tax Reform for Acceleration and Inclusion Act (TRAIN - R.A.No.10963) by further addressing the inequality in our taxation system; Proposes the lowering of corporate income tax rate, reforming the corporate income tax system, broadening the tax base by modernizing investment tax incentives, removing excessive tax exemptions and privileges given to certain industries, and limiting the grant of tax incentives to strategic industries and lagging regions.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : TRAIN 2</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>CUA, DAKILA CARLO E., ABU, RANEO &quot;RANIE&quot; E., GONZALES, AURELIO &quot;DONG&quot; JR. D.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-03-21</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>MOTHER BILL:&nbspHB08083</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON WAYS AND MEANS ON 2018-05-15</td></tr></table>